    "department": "Growth",
    "description": "Cluely makes great videos. It's a huge part of what we do.\n\nWe're always looking for exceptional talent who can help us take our videos to the next level.\n\nThis role is right for you if you understand cinematography, lighting, directing, and everything in-between intricately, have a history of making movies or short films, and love everything content.\n\nYou must have a strong sense of humor. A large part of the interview process will be us determining if you are funny and capable of generating videos that make people laugh.\n\nYou must be a strong generalist who can make things happen. If you have an idea, you will often not have a production assistant to help you make it happen.\n\nIf you want to make a podcast, it'll be on you to create the scene, buy the props, set up the lighting, buy the microphones, and everything in between.\n\nYou must also be comfortable working 12 hours a day 6 days a week. This will likely be the most intense job of your life.\n\nYou will live a block away from the office and spend most, if not all, of your waking hours working with a young and energetic team.\n\nIn return, you get\n\n - 150k-200k cash salary + equity\n\n - Free housing\n\n - Free food\n\n - To work at an extremely fast moving early stage tech startup\n\n - To get connected with huge influencers\n\n - A guaranteed girlfriend/boyfriend after 1 year",
